title: #92Noon! Alex Stalock/Bowhunting Burnsie/Mike Florio/Bill Guerin/Sam Farmer/Aaron Gleeman
description: PA is joined by goal tender for the Minnesota Wild, Alex Stalock. Later by Ryan Bowhunting Burnsie Burns to talk college football and then Pro Football Talk's Mike Florio. GM for the Minnesota Wild Bill Guerin is in studio. Then it's sports writer, Sam Farmer. And finally an in studio visit from Aaron Techie Gleeman to talk some Twins.
